songs.title: Lil Angel
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics From Snippet

[Intro]
This one is for the ones we love, yeah
Lil angel, lil angel

[Verse]
California helped me write this song (okay)
Don't nobody wanna wait that long (no way)
We just wanna find the ones we love (that's right)
Lil angel coming down from above (okay)
Lil angel coming down for the drugs
